description: This URL performs a job search on Google's careers site. It includes the following parameters: (1) 'q' is set to 'software engineer', specifying the job title or keyword to search for; (2) 'employment_type' is set to 'FULL_TIME', filtering for full-time positions only; (3) 'location' is repeated four times for 'United States', 'India', 'Poland', and 'Taiwan', meaning the search includes jobs in all these regions; (4) 'target_level' is repeated three times for 'ADVANCED', 'MID', and 'EARLY', indicating the search includes senior, mid-level, and entry-level positions.
